97889.overview: An assistant greenskeeper invites friends for a country club birthday party. A killer dressed as a greenskeeper crashes the party and kills people with golf tools.
97889.title: The Greenskeeper

19085.overview: Vulgar is about a man who is a children's clown but has not been getting much luck lately. He lives in a cheap apartment which he can't even afford. Bums are constantly sleeping in his run down car and crashing on his lawn. He has a nagging mother who lives in a nursing home, and his best friend is a moocher. One day he comes up with the idea to become a bachelor clown.
19085.title: Vulgar

71147.overview: This made-for-TV movie follows a group of friends as they try to find a boat lost for 50 years in the Bermuda Triangle.
71147.title: The Triangle

1872.overview: A reporter on the trail of a sinister cult wakes up in a morgue to find herself a member of the undead. She goes on a personal vendetta for a group a cultists that are responsible for her death.
1872.title: Rise: Blood Hunter

25579.overview: Two clans of deranged males make the mistake of stalking four young women they assume to be easy prey, only to find out that at the stroke of midnight the tables will be turned and all hell will break loose.
25579.title: Wicked Lake

49706.overview: A woman will go to whatever lengths necessary to obtain her dream home with a view of the sea. This includes driving down the property value and decreasing the occupancy rate by killing her potential neighbors ...
49706.title: Dream Home

479755.overview: After his wife Lucy walks out on him, Alexander tries to seek solace in alcohol and drugs, but the pain just won't go away. He is given the address of a mysterious man who claims to have the answer; a strange, powerful narcotic that will take away his anguish. Alexander can't take any more so he visits the dealer and is given the drug. For a while he feels fine, life is good again, until he realizes that shadowy figures are pursuing him. He tries to escape but there is no hiding from the Ingression.
479755.title: Ingression

31541.overview: When the mummified remains of an evil Egyptian queen are brought back to life, she resurrects an army of living dead to help fulfill the prophecy that promises her all the powers of the Underworld.
31541.title: Legion of the Dead

86703.overview: A Semester at Sea ship is attacked and sunk by a mutated two-headed shark, and the survivors seek refuge on a deserted atoll. The coeds, however, are no longer safe when the atoll starts flooding.
86703.title: 2-Headed Shark Attack

282070.overview: Alien pods come to Earth and, naturally, start taking over Human Hosts. One such pod only manages to take over one human's, Shin Izumi, right arm. Together they grow and co-exist, all the while the other aliens are making meals of other humans; Shin feels he must put a stop to it all, but his alien, Migi, doesn't see why.
282070.title: Parasyte: Part 2

445218.overview: Six college students go into the wetlands to find their missing professor after he takes off in search of the mythical and deadly monster known as the 'Swamp Freak.'
445218.title: Swamp Freak

446360.overview: A group of international students explores a basement that has been abandoned for years. But what starts off as an exploratory séance ends in bloody mayhem when a malicious entity is summoned.
446360.title: The Basement

784630.overview: A group of friends explore an abandoned factory out of curiosity, only to find out they are not alone.
784630.title: The Factory

460378.original_title: กัดกระชากเกรียน
460378.overview: Thailand gets infected with an epidemic that turns people into zombies that rage around the city. A group of teenage boys gets trapped in a hospital during the zombie outbreak. They will do whatever it takes to survive the hungry and brutal siege.
460378.title: Zombie Fighters

660175.overview: A young artist, imprisoned within the trammels of opium addiction, relives his phantasmagorical courtship with a mysterious Soprano known only as Ligeia. While exploring these opium induced memories, the lines dividing reality and fantasy, memory and hallucination, begin to blur into an indecipherable labyrinth of obsession and despair. Though he is nursed back to health by a new love, the Lady Rowena, the haunting of Ligeia's memories as well as the spirits of Azrael and Nehushtan, continue to plague his mind and soul.
660175.title: Edgar Allen Poe's Ligeia

546724.overview: Three best friends attending a heavy-metal show cross paths with sadistic killers after they travel to a secluded country home for an after party.
546724.title: We Summon the Darkness

773982.overview: A plucky student stumbles upon the secret life of young monsters who come out to learn and play when night falls at her elementary school.
773982.title: Spookiz: The Movie

552322.original_title: The Huntress: Rune of the Dead
552322.overview: When Runa’s father disappears on a viking journey she steps up as head of her family, but she is tormented by strange nightmares. One day when she is out hunting, she stumbles across a wounded warrior who carries news of her father, new that seem connected to her dreams. Something is coming for them, something vile.
552322.title: The Huntress: Rune of the Dead

749645.overview: An engaged Hollywood agent receives a mysterious letter for an anonymous sexual encounter and becomes ensnared in a sinister world of lying, infidelity, and digital data.
749645.title: The Beta Test

1079837.overview: So, what might happen if you were stuck late at school when the zombie apocalypse happens? What's going on? Is this all part of some twisted experiment the professor is conducting on the kids? Did the crazy Cook do it? Will they see tomorrow? Well, that's the situation our group of high-schoolers find themselves in, in "Undeaducated".
1079837.title: Undeaducated
